<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>ANEX Ачинск — подбор туров</title>

<style>
body {margin:0;font-family:Arial;background:#f4f6f8;}
.header {
 background:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507525428034-b723cf961d3e') center/cover;
 height:90vh;color:white;
}
.overlay {background:rgba(0,0,0,0.6);height:100%;padding:20px;}

.search-box {
 background:white;padding:20px;border-radius:12px;
 max-width:900px;margin:100px auto;
 display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;
}

.search-box input,.search-box select {
 padding:12px;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #ccc;flex:1;
}

.search-box button {
 background:#e30613;color:white;border:none;
 padding:15px;border-radius:8px;
}

.section {padding:50px 20px;text-align:center;}
.cards {display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:20px;justify-content:center;}

.card {
 background:white;width:280px;border-radius:12px;
 overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}
.card img {width:100%;height:180px;object-fit:cover;}
.card-body {padding:15px;}

.form {max-width:400px;margin:auto;background:white;padding:25px;border-radius:12px;}
input,textarea {
 width:100%;padding:12px;margin:10px 0;
 border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #ccc;
}

button {
 width:100%;padding:15px;
 background:#e30613;color:white;border:none;border-radius:8px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="header">
<div class="overlay">
<h1>ANEX Ачинск</h1>
<p>Подберем тур дешевле, чем в интернете</p>

<div class="search-box">
<input placeholder="Откуда (Красноярск)">
<input placeholder="Куда (Турция, Египет)">
<input type="date">
<select>
<option>7 ночей</option>
<option>10 ночей</option>
</select>
<button onclick="document.getElementById('form').scrollIntoView()">Найти тур</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="section">
<h2>Популярные направления</h2>
<div class="cards">
<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1526772662000-3f88f10405ff">
<div class="card-body"><h3>Турция</h3></div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1501785888041-af3ef285b470">
<div class="card-body"><h3>Египет</h3></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="section" id="form">
<h2>Оставьте заявку</h2>
<div class="form">
<input placeholder="Ваше имя">
<input placeholder="Телефон">
<textarea placeholder="Куда хотите"></textarea>
<button>Отправить</button>
</div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
